<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_508" id="253v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_508_r1l23"><expan>Wılh<ex>elm</ex></expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Sawnſheim Amptman cʒü Spekfelt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_508_r1l24">Lıeber VVilhalm / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt auf das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_508_r1l25">als wir <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Hohenloch vmb geleitte <expan>yecʒund<ex>e</ex>n</expan> in </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_508_r1l26">die meſʒ vnd <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> daraws <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>gepet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_508_r1l27">Jr vns 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> ſein </del> an <expan>ſeın<ex>er</ex></expan> ſtat ein <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> getan habt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_508_r1l28">wie das etlıch die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> für varen vnd keins geleittes <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_508_r1l29">noch <expan>neme<ex>n</ex></expan> vvöllen / 
<del rend="strikethrough">vnd daʒ Jr </del> <expan>Laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>vviſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_508_r1l30">daʒ vvir ſie des nicht geheiſʒen <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / . vnd wir <expan>empfelh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_508_r1l31">den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / daʒ ſie geleitte <expan>vord<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vnd nemen vnd on geleitt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_508_r1l32">nicht varen / vnd <expan>bitt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ew vnd getrawen <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> wol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_508_r1l33">Jr laſſet ew die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>darynne<ex>n</ex></expan> bevolhen ſein / . vnd daʒ Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_508_r1l34">vns die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vvelıche <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> fürgevaren ſein vnd nicht geleitte </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_508_r1l35"><expan>neme<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vvolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / mitnamen <expan>beſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>wiſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> laſſet / So <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_508_r1l36">ſie darvmb wol cʒe rede ſecʒen / vnd vvo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_508_r1l37">vnd dinſt etc <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>vts<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_508" id="253v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Wilh<ex>elm</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Sawnsheim, amptman czü Spekfelt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber Wilhalm, als ir uns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt
                        auf das, als wir <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Hohenloch umb geleitte
                            <expan>yeczund<ex>e</ex>n</expan> in die mesz und
                            <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> daraws
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                            <expan>gepet<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und ir uns an <expan>sein<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        stat ein <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> getan habt, wie das etlich die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> für varen und keins geleittes
                                <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> noch <expan>neme<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        wöllen, <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewr
                            <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz wir sie des nicht geheiszen
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>; und wir
                            <expan>empfelh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>,
                        daz sie geleitte <expan>vord<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und nemen und on geleitt
                        nicht varen, und <expan>bitt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ew und getrawen
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> wol, ir lasset ew die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>darynne<ex>n</ex></expan> bevolhen sein und daz ir uns die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, weliche <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        fürgevaren sein und nicht geleitte <expan>neme<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, mit namen <expan>beschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan> lasset, so <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                        sie darumb wol cze rede seczen. Und wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb und dinst etc.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>ut s<ex>upra.</ex></expan></ab>
</div>
</div></body>
